Control Overview
<font face=aircut3/12 color=#ffffff>
<p>
Tracks will popup a list of all the tracks and allow you to play one. Repeat
doesn't do anything yet. Config will eventually allow you to configure the
epplet, but right now merely forces an update of the CD information.
